Name: HEARTBEAT
Description: A periodic heartbeat to indicate that the system is still running.

Name: RESPONSE
Description: A response to a telecommand with the response data.

Name: DATA1
Description: The first part of the telemetry of the system.

Name: DATA2
Description: The second part of the telemetry of the system.

Name: DATA3
Description: The third part of the telemetry of the system.

Name: DATA_RECOVERY
Description: The data generated by the recovery thread once in the RECOVERY state.
